      <title>加拿大和澳大利亚加强关键矿产合作</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/canada-australia-boost-collaboration-critical-minerals-2024-03-04/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大和澳大利亚在周一的联合声明中表示，已同意促进与关键矿物的开采、加工和精炼相关的共同优先事项。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/canada-australia-boost-collaboration-critical-minerals-2024-03-04/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 16:49:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苏里南国家石油公司与马来西亚国家石油公司、埃克森美孚签署天然气勘探协议</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/surinames-staatsolie-signs-gas-exploration-deal-with-petronas-exxon-2024-03-04/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苏里南国家石油公司周一表示，马来西亚国家石油公司和美国石油巨头埃克森美孚已同意扩大其沿海天然气发现的勘探范围，并正在考虑浮动液化天然气项目的潜力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/surinames-staatsolie-signs-gas-exploration-deal-with-petronas-exxon-2024-03-04/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 16:39:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴基斯坦伊姆兰·汗支持的政党拒绝保留议会席位 - 裁决</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/pakistans-imran-khan-backed-party-not-eligible-reserved-parliament-seats-poll-2024-03-04/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴基斯坦选举委员会周一裁定，与前总理伊姆兰·汗支持的候选人结盟的政党没有资格在立法机构中获得额外保留席位，这对该陷入困境的组织的执政前景再次构成打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/pakistans-imran-khan-backed-party-not-eligible-reserved-parliament-seats-poll-2024-03-04/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 12:46:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴基斯坦谢巴兹·谢里夫宣誓就任总理</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/pakistans-shehbaz-sharif-takes-oath-prime-minister-2024-03-04/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴基斯坦谢赫巴兹·谢里夫周一宣誓，第二次正式就任总理，此前近四个星期，全国选举的不确定性导致联合政府的组建被推迟。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/pakistans-shehbaz-sharif-takes-oath-prime-minister-2024-03-04/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 10:33:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>越南首都河内名列污染最严重城市榜首</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/vietnamese-capital-hanoi-tops-list-most-polluted-cities-2024-03-04/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一，越南首都河内的街道笼罩在浓浓的烟雾中，由于车辆排放的高浓度颗粒物和建筑相关的细尘造成空气污染，能见度大大降低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/environment/vietnamese-capital-hanoi-tops-list-most-polluted-cities-2024-03-04/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 10:20:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新加坡收紧雇用外国专业人士的规定</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/singapore-tightens-rules-hiring-foreign-professionals-2024-03-04/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新加坡政府周一宣布，将从明年开始提高公司雇用的外国高管和专业人士的薪资标准。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/singapore-tightens-rules-hiring-foreign-professionals-2024-03-04/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 08:41:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>政府官员称特斯拉正在与泰国就生产设施进行谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-has-conducted-site-survey-thailand-ev-facility-says-government-official-2024-03-04/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国总理办公室的一位官员周一表示，电动汽车 (EV) 制造商特斯拉去年年底进行了现场勘察，目前正在与泰国政府就在该国建立潜在生产设施进行谈判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-has-conducted-site-survey-thailand-ev-facility-says-government-official-2024-03-04/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 08:31:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>首尔情报机构称朝鲜闯入韩国芯片设备公司</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korea-broke-into-s-korean-chip-equipment-firms-seouls-spy-agency-says-2024-03-04/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国间谍机构周一表示，朝鲜的黑客组织已侵入至少两家韩国芯片制造设备制造商，因为该国希望逃避制裁并为武器计划生产自己的半导体。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/north-korea-broke-into-s-korean-chip-equipment-firms-seouls-spy-agency-says-2024-03-04/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 08:30:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马科斯表示，如果海洋利益被忽视，菲律宾将反击中国</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-will-push-back-against-china-if-maritime-interests-ignored-marcos-2024-03-04/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[菲律宾总统小费迪南德·马科斯周一表示，菲律宾将在有争议的南海问题上与中国合作，但如果其主权和海洋权利被忽视，菲律宾将予以反击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-will-push-back-against-china-if-maritime-interests-ignored-marcos-2024-03-04/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 07:43:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尼泊尔总理组建新联盟，抛弃旧盟友</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/nepal-coalition-crisis-pm-talks-with-opposition-new-alliance-2024-03-04/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼泊尔总理普什帕·卡迈勒·达哈尔周一任命了三名部长，其中两个反对党各一名，组成新的联盟，抛弃了在其前任政府中占主导地位的中间派尼泊尔国大党。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/nepal-coalition-crisis-pm-talks-with-opposition-new-alliance-2024-03-04/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 04 Mar 2024 07:41:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
